In view of the above, Approval is hereby accorded for an Extension of Time from 15-12-2021 to 31-12-2022 (381 days) without Liquidated Damages with Price Adjustment and without any type of claim. The Executive Engineer, Project Office, and PMC Consultant recommended the Extension of Time due to the following reasons. 
1. The required ROW has been affected in certain sections due to hindrances. 
2. Delay in permission to fell trees within ROW (June 2019 to April 2020; August 2020 to September 2021;November 2021 to December 2021). Permission awaited for 5 km
3. Execution of works taken up under variation.
4. Frequent shutdowns due to COVID pandemic. 
5. Once the lockdown was lifted, the labor migrated to their parent states.
6. Extended monsoon in 2021 spread over 6 months from July to December. 7. Unseasonal rains has affected the progress of works.

packageTimeExtensionDTOs.approvalRemarks:
By taking into account the initial delay on the part of RGHCL on account of land disputes; Environmental clearance etc., as well as the consequences of the COVID-l9 pandemic situation for which GOI/ GOK itself had permitted six months extension for
the ongoing works, it becomes necessary/ imperative to grant EOT to complete the project.

1. However, even during this period also the contractors could not complete the works. The reasons for the same are certain amount of delay on the part of contractors to mobilize/procure the required resources especially specialized shuttering in time in terms of Mile Stone requirement. And the same got compounded further due to the effects of COVID -19 pandemic situation especially in respect of availability of human resources and increase in cost of materials etc
2. In these contracts for the compensation events due to RGHCL's delay only extension of time for completion of work is only provided and specially stipulates that compensation events shall not entitle the contractors to claim financially whatsoever.
4. Further these contracts being fixed price lumpsum contract for the extended period also no price adjustment shall be considered/available
5. And another major/main factor that was hindering the progress of work is abnormal delay in payment of the running bills,
